Construct a php program to create a chess board in PHP using the “For” loop.

code:
<?php
echo "<div style='width:320px;'>";
for ($row = 1; $row <= 8; $row++) {
    for ($col = 1; $col <= 8; $col++) {
        $color = ($row + $col) % 2 ? "#000" : "#fff";
        echo "<div style='width:40px;height:40px;float:left;background:$color;'></div>";
    }
}
echo "</div>";
?>
